---
title: Venison, Beef & Bacon Lasagne with Red Wine Jus & Radish Salad
description: Layers of ooey-gooey 'béchamel' sauce and beef, venison and bacon are filled to the brim in this winning dish! Topped with Cheddar cheese and served with a fresh radish salad, this is a pub classic, turned hearty home cooking at its finest!
